  243. (** For [array_indexing ?typ log2size ptr ofs dbg] :
  244.     Produces a pointer to the element of the array [ptr] on the position [ofs]
  245.     with the given element [log2size] log2 element size. [ofs] is given as a
  246.     tagged int expression.
  247.     The optional ?typ argument is the C-- type of the result.
  248.     By default, it is Addr, meaning we are constructing a derived pointer
  249.     into the heap.  If we know the pointer is outside the heap
  250.     (this is the case for bigarray indexing), we give type Int instead. *)
  251. ‌val array_indexing :
